						               													<description>As a tour guide in Citytrip Brugge you want to create the most memorable trip by visiting famous buildings and musea, events, restaurants and more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Citytrip Brugge is a flip &amp;amp; write game that is quick to setup and easy to play. With a basic and advanced scoresheet, 23 starting points and 44 different missions, no 2 games will feel the same!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One player flips the upper card of the action stack. Simultaneously everybody chooses 2 actions that are horizontally or vertically adjacent (=7 possible combinations). Each player creates a road and circles achieved goals which give points on the scoresheet. The game ends after 15 turns. The player with the highest satisfaction score wins Citytrip Brugge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash; description from the designer &amp;mdash;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
